data.description: Welcome home to this 3 bedroom, 2.5 bathroom home on serene private lot with NO HOA! The family room with fireplace, dining, large kitchen boasting a breakfast area and walk-in pantry, plus a main floor half bath for guests make this home perfect for entertaining. The primary bedroom has an en-suite bathroom with double vanity and soaking tub with separate shower. The 2 additional guests rooms share a full bathroom. Outside this property shines with tons of privacy and a storage outbuilding. Schedule your showing today!
